    <h1>Local Link Building</h1>
    <p class="description">The practice of earning backlinks from websites with geographic relevance to your business. Moz identifies link signals as the <strong>#1 factor for local organic rankings</strong> and #2 for local pack rankings.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
